{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"843f295f-5c7e-4d2e-ace1-4069148cbe1e","content":"With **MSTest.Sdk 3.8.0**, the switch is minimal:\n\n1. **Remove (or delete) the `<UseVSTest>` property** from your project/`Directory.Build.props`:\n\n   ```xml\n   <!-- Remove this line -->\n   <UseVSTest>true</UseVSTest>\n   ```\n\n   Microsoft.Testing.Platform is the **default** runner in MSTest.Sdk ≥ 3.2, so removing the opt-in to VSTest is all that's needed.\n\n2. **Run tests** the same way:\n   ```\n   dotnet test\n   ```\n\n**Things to watch for:**\n\n- **Command-line options** differ — VSTest switches like `--filter` become `--filter` still works but some others (e.g., `--logger`) use a new syntax (`--report-trx`).\n- **`.runsettings`** — still supported, but platform-specific extensions use `[TestProperty]` or CLI args instead.\n- If you relied on **VSTest adapters/extensions**, check for Microsoft.Testing.Platform equivalents (e.g., `Microsoft.Testing.Extensions.TrxReport`).\n\nThat single property removal is the only project-file change required.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"ac894afa-445c-41f7-ad18-85e38c071fdc","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about migrating from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform in their MSTest project that uses MSTest.Sdk/3.8.0. This is a knowledge question about .NET testing configuration, not a code change request in their repository. Let me provide a concise answer based on my knowledge.\n\nWith MSTest.Sdk, the migration from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform is straightforward:\n\n1. Remove `<UseVSTest>true</UseVSTest>` from the project file (or set it to `false`)\n2. That's essentially it for MSTest.Sdk 3.8.0, since Microsoft.Testing.Platform is the default runner starting from MSTest.Sdk 3.2+\n\n\n3. The main differences are in the CLI experience and how command-line options work, plus any custom extensions or adapters may need adjustments to work with the new platform.","outputTokens":525,"requestId":"6808:1FDBAC:75F498:7D43A1:6A044D48"},"id":"59346554-9c9f-4926-bdba-1d10e60b1353","timestamp":"2026-05-13T10:07:25.103Z","parentId":"97489679-cae4-4bae-98d7-87641b2a43a0"}
